text: Évora District ( ) is located in Alentejo, in southern Portugal. The district capital is the city of Évora. ==Municipalities== The district is composed by 14 municipalities: * Alandroal * Arraiolos * Borba * Estremoz * Évora * Montemor-o-Novo * Mora * Mourão * Olivença (de facto in Spain; note that Talega is administered separately from Olivença by Spanish Authorities*) * Portel * Redondo * Reguengos de Monsaraz * Vendas Novas * Viana do Alentejo * Vila
